Sure, here are some examples:

1. Trenutno *treniram* za maraton. (Currently *training* for a marathon.)
2. U ovoj *trenutnoj* situaciji, moramo biti oprezni. (In this *current* situation, we need to be careful.)
3. Molim te da mi odgovoriš u *trenu*. (Please respond to me *right away*.)
4. *Trenutak* odluke je došao. (The *moment* of decision has come.)
5. Sve je bilo gotovo u *trenu*. (Everything was over in an *instant*.)
6. *Trenutak* je da se pozdravimo. (It's *time* to say goodbye.)
7. Nisam mogao da vidim ništa u *trenu*. (I couldn't see anything in a *flash*.)
8. Budi tu za mene u svakom *trenu*. (Be there for me in every *moment*.)
9. Sjajna ideja mi je pala na *tren*. (A great idea came to me in an *instant*.)
10. Molim te da me *trenutno* ostaviš na miru. (Please leave me alone *right now*.)

I hope this helps!